Cambodia is here.

10
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:29,610
Ream is here.

11
00:00:29,610 --> 00:00:31,310
Now if the Chinese Communist Party’s military,

12
00:00:31,310 --> 00:00:32,750
the People’s Liberation Army,

13
