was really building a navy base in Cambodia—

14
00:00:35,809 --> 00:00:37,109
that would be a big deal.

15
00:00:37,109 --> 00:00:38,949
But don’t worry!

16
00:00:38,949 --> 00:00:40,079
Because last November,

17
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:43,600
Cambodia’s Prime Minister Hun Sen totally
denied it!

18
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:46,260
Of course, it would be super embarrassing
if, say,

19
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:48,569
